<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="recently-adv">recently <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'riːsntli/    美 /'riːsntli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>近来；最近</strong></h4>
<p>not long ago：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I caught a bad cold recently. 
我最近得了重感冒。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Chinese scientists <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (recent) had a chance to study a wild female panda with a newborn baby.  （2016 四川）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. recently  </p></div>